article_id:3235,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The newly added 5★ adventurers Bondforged Zethia and Bondforged Prince will also appear in subsequent summon showcases.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Any Gala adventurer or dragon added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase. For information about which adventurers and dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Please note that only the following adventurers (and no dragons) are featured in this summon showcase.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><br></span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The Scratch-A-Thon Summon that is live at the same time does not include the newly added featured adventurers appearing in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Bondforged Zethia (light/wand)</div><div>5★ Bondforged Prince (wind/sword)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from this Gala Dragalia summon showcase cannot be redeemed in the Gala Dragalia that was available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706399"></span>.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.00% (Adventurers: 1.00%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 5.00% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 3.00%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
