			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>Zethia, having awakened to the power of bonds.<br>Using the powers of an Auspex and Bahamut,<br>she fights with her friends to save the world.<br>She now has both the ability to fight and the<br>strength of heart to stand tall on her own.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5299b6045ba548739b1b50f5c8e92a442.png"></span>
				<span>Blazing Fount</span>
				<div class="skill-cost">
					<span>Shareable</span>
					<div class="txt-num">
						<span>5</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies<br>and inflicts flashburn.<br><br>If the user has Power of Bonds, this skill will<br>instead deal damage to the target and nearby<br>enemies, dispel one buff from each of them,<br>and inflict flashburn. The user will be immune<br>to knockback during this attack.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 800 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,800<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 7,980<br>Special Effects:<br>・Flashburn<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br><br><color=#00008B>When the User Has Power of Bonds:</color><br>Damage: 1,800 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 360 × 5 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,800<br>Special Effects:<br>・Flashburn<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41.6<br>・Dispels Buffs</div></dd><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/0e22dbd42118a954d53624bdb6620ad22.png"></span>
				<span>Ring of Affection</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Grants all teammates the "Power of Bonds" effect.<br>If an adventurer has Power of Bonds, when that<br>adventurer would take damage greater than or<br>equal to their remaining HP, that damage is<br>nullified, the effect is consumed, and damage<br>is instead dealt to the rest of the user's team.<br>This damage equals 20% of each teammate's<br>maximum HP.<br><br>If the user has Power of Bonds, this skill will<br>instead restore HP to all teammates and remove<br>Power of Bonds from the entire team.</div><div class="skill-detail">Skill Energy Required: 4,200<br>Special Effects:<br>・Power of Bonds<br>　　Does not stack<br><br><color=#00008B>When the User Has Power of Bonds:</color><br>Skill Energy Required: 0<br>Recovery Potency: 100</div></dd></dl></div>
	<div class="exAbility explanation">
		<div class="title">Co-ability</div>
		<dl>
			<dt>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span>
