<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/24d7c6c7bc433277432a054dad84fd452.png"></span><span>Windwyrm's Dragonlight II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user a unique force strike that deals<br>damage to enemies in a line. Performing this<br>force strike during a standard attack then<br>immediately following it with another standard<br>attack will resume the user's standard attack<br>combo from their most recent attack.<br><br>If this unique force strike is performed while<br>in midair during the fourth attack in the user's<br>standard attack combo, a powered up variant<br>that deals more damage will be used instead.<br><br>When shapeshifting, the user will transform<br>into Primal Midgardsormr regardless of what<br>dragon they are equipped with. Primal<br>Midgardsormr's dragon skill level will match<br>the level of the adventurer's initial skill,<br>displayed at the top of their skill list.<br><br>Shapeshifting will grant the entire team a<br>team critical damage amp with a maximum<br>team amp level of three.<br><br>When in dragon form, the user's attacks are<br>granted the ability to dispel one enemy buff.<br>This effect does not apply to the damage<br>dealt as the user shapeshifts.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/857a2a2fdbc31b188c91fbd6f6eca6b32.png"></span><span>Unbreakable Bonds II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freeze and bog by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/de137cf7302f5717d1be863dbd4a45e62.png"></span><span>Tempest Charge II</span></dt><dd><div>Fills 50% of the dragon gauge when the user's<br>HP drops to 40% (once per quest) and reduces<br>dragon gauge depletion over time by 20%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.</div><div>・The adventurer Bondforged Prince&#39;s skills cannot be shared.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div>・For details on the Power of Bonds effect, please see the in-game Help section.</div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Bondforged Prince&#39;s Standard Attacks and Skills</div><div>Abilities that increase damage dealt while shapeshifted (such as Dragon Damage +X%) and abilities that grant effects to attacks performed while shapeshifted (such as Windwyrm&#39;s Dragonlight) apply to the fifth attack in Bondforged Prince&#39;s standard attack combo and the attacks performed by Primal Midgardsormr when the skills Blazing Tempest and Vortex Circlet are used.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase are on sale and cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648706400,update_time1648602456